Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.18,0:00:06.48,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}nakushita yakusoku wa hoshi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.18,0:00:06.48,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}Send the lost promises to the stars
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.73,0:00:12.82,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}omoide wa tokenai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.73,0:00:12.82,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}My memories won't fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.37,0:00:27.54,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,yotsuba no clover sagashinagara kimi no kao
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.37,0:00:27.54,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I steal a glance at you as we look for four-leaf clovers,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.75,0:00:33.72,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,chirari nusumi mite wa me o sorasu
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.75,0:00:33.72,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,But then divert my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.17,0:00:39.22,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,yasashii ame wa furu watashitachi no ue ni
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.17,0:00:39.22,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,The gentle rain falls above our heads
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.22,0:00:44.77,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,surechigau hito no kazu dake dramatic ni naru no
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.22,0:00:44.77,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,as it becomes as dramatic as the number of people passing by
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.06,0:00:50.27,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,kowareta taisetsu na mono to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.06,0:00:50.27,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if we'll ever be able to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.57,0:00:56.53,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,itsuka mata aeru hi ga kurukashira
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.57,0:00:56.53,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,reunite with those precious things that were broken
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.82,0:01:01.87,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,nokoshita kizuato ga kienai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.82,0:01:01.87,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,The scars that were left behind won't go away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.16,0:01:07.58,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,sorezore no basho made
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.16,0:01:07.58,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we must depart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.04,0:01:11.34,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,mou ikanakucha
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.04,0:01:11.34,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,To our own separate ways
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.16,0:01:37.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was still little...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.21,0:01:46.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,One day, riding the green bike I always used to ride, I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.59,0:01:52.80,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,"How far can I go without turning back?"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.76,0:01:55.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now I sometimes wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.22,0:02:02.15,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly was I trying to do at that time?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.19,0:02:07.40,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Once again, it was no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.32,0:02:09.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Takemoto...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.28,0:02:12.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, so you failed your employment exam again...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.91,0:02:15.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm sorry, it seems you have a guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.41,0:02:19.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm an alumni of this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.75,0:02:21.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Usui.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.87,0:02:25.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice to meet you. I'm Takemoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.00,0:02:27.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He was actually one of my students.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.88,0:02:31.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He runs a custom-order furniture business, and\Nhe might not look it, but he's president.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.09,0:02:34.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, what do you mean by "he might not look it"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.01,0:02:38.85,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, this thing is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.85,0:02:40.02,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.02,0:02:41.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a custom-made rotating shelf.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.52,0:02:45.10,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll finally save me from the avalanche of spray cans.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.77,0:02:46.98,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So, how much is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.32,0:02:48.07,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,500,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.07,0:02:48.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Expensive!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.82,0:02:49.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, 20,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.57,0:02:50.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheap!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.57,0:02:53.24,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, is your company really all right with you being so laidback?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.24,0:02:54.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Beats me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.03,0:02:55.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,"Beats me"?! Hey now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.62,0:02:58.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on. Let me do some calculations.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.45,0:03:03.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The cost for supplies, construction,\Ntransportation, and installation...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.37,0:03:05.38,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.46,0:03:07.79,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.05,0:03:11.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.92,0:03:12.80,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How much?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.80,0:03:15.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't talk like you're buying some vegetable.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.39,0:03:17.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Takemoto-kun, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.26,0:03:19.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to come work for my company?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.02,0:03:23.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Usui! Like I said, you're being too simple-minded!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.60,0:03:26.52,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,First, you need to properly explain what the\Ncompany's about and what the job entails...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.94,0:03:29.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Takemoto! You don't need to rush to make a reply!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.19,0:03:31.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hire me, pretty please!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.78,0:03:32.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. You're hired.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.24,0:03:38.70,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, well, a lot has happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.70,0:03:40.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But he's tentatively been hired.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.41,0:03:40.37,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial\shad0\bord0.1\be1\fscx85\fs28\pos(378,125)\c&H61676F&\3c&H61676F&}Takemoto-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.41,0:03:40.37,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\be1\shad0\fscx65\fsp1\pos(322,200)\3c&HD9E2E9&\c&H6E777E&\frz354.821}Congratulations on your Employment
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.83,0:03:42.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,For the sake of Takemoto-kun's future...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.12,0:03:43.96,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.96,0:03:44.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.08,0:03:48.79,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for worrying everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.09,0:03:55.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the company that I'll be working for makes\Ncustom-made furniture and remodels homes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.55,0:03:59.39,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And since I like woodworking, I'm happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.14,0:04:00.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.26,0:04:02.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.72,0:04:06.73,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, when the acceptance comes, it comes so easily, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.06,0:04:10.27,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, and I was so worried at one point...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.90,0:04:14.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama-senpai... thank you so much...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.65,0:04:19.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Usui's place is a small company that a\Nsmall group of Hamabi graduates made...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.82,0:04:21.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But since Usui is a little strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.24,0:04:26.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There should be a lot of fun jobs, and I think you\Nshould be able to work happily, Takemoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.54,0:04:31.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear that just earlier, they reformed some rich guy's\Nvacation home and turned it into a ninja estate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.88,0:04:33.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They did stuff like make a huge maze in the yard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.46,0:04:36.38,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like fun, doesn't it, Takemoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.09,0:04:39.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I'm excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.34,0:04:39.80,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? Hanamoto residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.76,0:04:44.68,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuu-chan! Phone call for you! It's Usui-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.68,0:04:46.52,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, speak of the devil...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.06,0:04:50.81,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.52,0:04:54.69,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we're all celebrating for Takemoto right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.86,0:04:56.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.49,0:05:00.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That rich dude gave his creditors the\Nslip and the ninja estate got seized?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.82,0:05:05.62,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,800)\3c&H746FAE&\fsp20\fscy95\shad0\bord0.8\fs76\fnAlsina Ultrajada\be1\c&H7569AA&\frz30\pos(418,62)}S{\frz10}T{\frz-10}O{\frz-30}P
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.70,0:05:04.79,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The deposit vanished and 42,000,000 yen was lost...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.29,0:05:08.50,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A-And your company...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.00,0:05:12.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, boy... I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.17,0:05:21.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm e-e-e-extremely so-sorry to be saying this wh-wh-while\Ny-you're all en-enjo-en-enjo-enjoying...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.64,0:05:26.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A-A-A-A-Actually, e-everyone, e-e-e-extremely unfortunate news...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.72,0:05:27.68,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.93,0:05:31.85,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, no more... I understand plenty already...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.44,0:05:35.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just drink happily tonight...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.03,0:05:40.49,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while since we all gathered, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.49,0:05:43.45,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial\shad0\bord0.1\be1\fscx85\fs23\c&H61676F&\3c&H61676F&\pos(432,99)}Takemoto-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.49,0:05:43.45,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord1\be1\shad0\fscx65\fsp0\fs22\frz357.618\3c&HD9E2E9&\c&H6E777E&\pos(227,150)}Party to Cheer up
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.45,0:05:45.70,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers for Takemoto-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.79,0:05:50.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.00,0:05:51.79,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the last straw...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.25,0:05:55.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so pitiful, I can't even think of words to say to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.25,0:05:57.55,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.92,0:05:59.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.51,0:06:02.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's a sample bowl.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.72,0:06:05.18,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nomiya-san from Fujiwara Design had asked me to make one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.18,0:06:08.39,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, you sure are working hard, Yamada-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.18,0:06:10.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.94,0:06:12.73,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I really have a long way to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.28,0:06:18.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.65,0:06:20.36,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The design sketch isn't done yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.36,0:06:23.36,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please turn down all appearance requests.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.03,0:06:24.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.24,0:06:28.62,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, allow me my solitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.21,0:06:35.21,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma... Mario...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.71,0:06:37.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Luigi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.88,0:06:39.38,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Mario...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.88,0:06:44.30,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If you take even the smallest pity on me, please listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.80,0:06:47.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...to the confession of your foolish brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.26,0:06:50.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Non...{\i0} I won't listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.43,0:06:53.10,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I beg you, Mario!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.10,0:06:54.81,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,For the love of God, please listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.31,0:06:58.52,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I was such a fool for leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.36,0:07:02.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Afterwards, I regretted what I did so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.57,0:07:04.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I already said that I won't listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.66,0:07:08.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, close those lips.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.45,0:07:10.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We're finished with our silly conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.33,0:07:13.54,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me have a better look at your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.92,0:07:15.79,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My precious shortie.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.54,0:07:17.63,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mario!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.04,0:07:20.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so foolish... look at how thin you've become.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.71,0:07:24.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I wanted to see you so badly...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.88,0:07:27.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shh. Don't speak another word.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.22,0:07:29.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand everything already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.39,0:07:31.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.85,0:07:35.81,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We can sum it up in two words: One in Body and Spirit...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.85,0:07:35.81,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Two words: {\be1\3c&H000000&}isshin doutai (一心　同体)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.36,0:07:40.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes! We're e-extremely sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.19,0:07:43.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you for real? That president...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.11,0:07:48.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that he would ditch all the jobs he took on in Tottori...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.91,0:07:49.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\fnArtificeSSK\b0\fscx65\fs30\fsp5\3c&HECFCFE&\c&H348FD2&\pos(90,122)}"Miwako-san,\Nget a hold of\Nyourself!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.54,0:07:53.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And so the jobs that he ditched in the middle are:
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.04,0:08:01.05,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,three residences, a remodeling of a nursery, and as\Nfor restaurants, there are Italian, French, African...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.05,0:08:02.63,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Tottori, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.63,0:08:05.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They're famous for Chinese scallion, pears, and deer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.63,0:08:08.80,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and they have snow crabs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.80,0:08:10.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Snow crabs are only during the winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.76,0:08:14.48,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then again, the work might actually\Ntake up until they're in season...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.48,0:08:16.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Whee, I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.02,0:08:18.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.35,0:08:19.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No, what are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.86,0:08:24.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we go? To eat some snow crabs...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.62,0:08:33.29,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Miwako-san, please hold onto my keys.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.58,0:08:38.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I had newspaper and mail delivery halted, but just in case\Nsomething else gets delivered there accidentally.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.00,0:08:42.38,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. But you totally lack sex appeal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.04,0:08:42.80,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\fnArtificeSSK\b0\fscx65\fs39\fsp5\3c&HECFCFE&\pos(427,377)\c&H208ED7&}"Are you going out, Nomiya-san?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.38,0:08:44.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You could've just had Yamada-san hold onto it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.13,0:08:48.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want her stinking up my room like a Nara pickle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.09,0:08:54.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um... Miwako-san, I was wondering\Nif you could hold onto my keys, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.35,0:08:59.73,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And actually, I'm perfectly okay with\Nyou using my room as you see fit...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.43,0:09:05.69,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\fnTimes New Roman\fscx80\b0\bord0\shad0\fs22\c&HCDD2D6&\pos(685,184)}\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hDo your best,\NYamazaki
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.39,0:09:05.69,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\fnTimes New Roman\fscx85\b0\bord0\shad0\fs21\c&HC9CED3&\pos(122,161)}\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hHang in there,\NYamazaki
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.73,0:09:05.69,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's actually a spare key, so you can\Ncontinue using it even after I get back...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.32,0:09:07.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? May I?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.74,0:09:10.24,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Of course you may!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.24,0:09:15.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Aren't you glad, Leader? We\Nhave a vacation home for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.74,0:09:16.20,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(550,0)\shad0\fnArtificeSSK\b0\fscx65\fs39\fsp5\3c&HECFCFE&\pos(431,373)\c&H208ED7&}"Vacation home. That sounds wonderful."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.20,0:09:18.12,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um, Miwako-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.12,0:09:20.33,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh ho? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.33,0:09:23.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We can sublease the property and obtain rent?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.17,0:09:27.55,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And with that money, the two of us can eat an\Nextra-large sirloin steak three times a week?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.55,0:09:28.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my Leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.97,0:09:30.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\fnArtificeSSK\b0\fscx65\fs39\fsp5\3c&HECFCFE&\pos(436,373)\c&H0689DC&}"Extra-large sirloin. That sounds wonderful."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.68,0:09:32.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be depressed, Yamazaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.39,0:09:36.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Miwako-san is an old geezer dressed up as a beautiful superior.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.14,0:09:39.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not saying that to hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.77,0:09:41.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.77,0:09:43.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Nomiya... What's the meaning of life?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.90,0:09:45.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.69,0:09:48.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you know firsthand when I find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.87,0:10:00.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's empty...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.67,0:10:07.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nomiya-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.46,0:10:09.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.72,0:10:11.05,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going out?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.05,0:10:12.18,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, for a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.89,0:10:16.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I made the samples of the dish and the bowl, so I've brought them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.01,0:10:17.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.06,0:10:18.73,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please hand them to Miwako-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.39,0:10:21.48,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There's some cake, so help yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.48,0:10:22.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.98,0:10:24.69,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll have some.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.90,0:10:26.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.48,0:10:29.07,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Nomiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.07,0:10:30.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.28,0:10:33.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, shall we drive?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.87,0:10:34.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.33,0:10:36.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I've brought the samples.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.99,0:10:38.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, good timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.95,0:10:42.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, so these are the cakes that Nomiya-san was talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.08,0:10:44.25,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you saw him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.71,0:10:46.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He just left for Tottori.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.42,0:10:48.21,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Tottori?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.67,0:10:50.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. A six-month tour of Tottori.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.30,0:10:52.47,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.64,0:11:01.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was little, I once thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.39,0:11:06.73,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,"How far can I go without turning back?"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.32,0:11:12.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what this sound is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.66,0:11:16.78,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been sticking in my head since earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.87,0:11:25.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.59,0:11:28.38,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.38,0:11:30.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The sound of emptiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.47,0:11:38.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Takemoto, you in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.39,0:11:41.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I got some mixed rice from Miwako-san, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.14,0:11:46.10,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Takemoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.63,0:12:13.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the ocean...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.09,0:12:15.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.80,0:12:18.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Where... am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.93,0:12:21.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Takemoto isn't coming home?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.06,0:12:23.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He hasn't been back for two nights.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.06,0:12:26.10,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He's left his bag in his room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.60,0:12:27.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What about his wallet?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.60,0:12:29.40,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like he took it with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.40,0:12:31.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And his bicycle is gone as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.19,0:12:35.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder where Takemoto-kun went?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.86,0:12:37.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It was raining the day before yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.45,0:12:41.24,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope he hasn't been in an accident or anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.24,0:12:43.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what happened to Takemoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.87,0:12:45.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.41,0:12:50.08,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H929C9F&\fnTimes New Roman\b0\shad0\fscx80\bord0\fs22\pos(412,33)}Job Searching
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.41,0:12:50.08,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H929C9F&\fnTimes New Roman\b0\shad0\fscx80\fsp-1\bord0\fs20\pos(161,108)}Collapse or\Nthe Tower of\NAdolescence
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.41,0:12:50.08,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H929C9F&\fnTimes New Roman\b0\shad0\fscx80\bord0\fs21\pos(72,238)}Bankruptcy\Nof the\Ncompany\Nthat\Nhired\Nhim
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.83,0:12:49.67,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, there are too many logical reasons...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.50,0:12:52.21,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Anguish and frustration, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.43,0:12:58.18,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.68,0:13:00.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that Takemoto...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.26,0:13:02.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it just occured to me as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.64,0:13:05.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Shuu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.14,0:13:07.52,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think of something, Mayama?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.52,0:13:10.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah, how should I put it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.94,0:13:15.49,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm thinking Takemoto is probably okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.49,0:13:16.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.53,0:13:18.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't the two of you worried about Takemoto?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.11,0:13:23.12,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, see, he might've just left to take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.74,0:13:27.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thinking we don't need to make a big fuss about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.04,0:13:29.62,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. How should we put it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.62,0:13:35.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He might've just felt like going on a trip by himself...\NOr rather there's something he wants to find...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.26,0:13:39.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Going on a journey by himself to find...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.59,0:13:42.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that Takemoto-kun left on a journey of self-realization?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.89,0:13:43.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamada, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.18,0:13:45.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't say it so plainly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.77,0:13:48.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Self-realization?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.02,0:13:50.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A journey...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.73,0:13:52.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We've heard, Hanamoto-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.44,0:13:55.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Takemoto-kun has left on a journey of self-realization?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.19,0:14:08.16,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fs24\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Loincloth:\N{\be1\3c&H000000&}Adolescence
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.94,0:13:57.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while since someone went on one!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.94,0:13:59.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Has it been five years?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.65,0:14:04.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Self-realization actually takes a lot of nerve.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.12,0:14:08.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure makes my heart leap!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.20,0:14:08.16,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\fs78\fnArtificeSSK\b0\fscx40\pos(426,89)\c&H615B4C&}Adolescence
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.16,0:14:12.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it. Why would Takemoto need to go looking for himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.29,0:14:13.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you just what you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.88,0:14:17.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Or could it be that Takemoto can't see himself right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.46,0:14:20.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, in a sense, he's spot on...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.55,0:14:25.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,More like, I'm thinking Takemoto would rather\Nnot be understood by you of all people...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.39,0:14:28.10,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder where Takemoto-kun is sleeping...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.10,0:14:30.77,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope he's eating properly...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.10,0:14:33.10,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to worry so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.77,0:14:37.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans are surprisingly hardy and persistent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.19,0:14:39.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay not to go look for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.90,0:14:45.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu, if you find a person who went off on a search\Nfor himself before he even finds himself...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.53,0:14:47.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then he won't have a place to come back to anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.70,0:14:51.29,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,As expected of you, Hanamoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.29,0:14:54.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Professor Tokudaiji! When did you get to Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.13,0:14:57.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, veterans sure see things in a different light.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.09,0:14:59.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.26,0:15:00.30,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.30,0:15:03.34,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that you went on one as well, Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.34,0:15:04.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,On a journey of self-realization?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.97,0:15:08.18,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy is a professional. He went seven times!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.18,0:15:09.77,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0.1\shad0\1a&H16&\fs78\fsp3\fnArtificeSSK\b0\fscx40\pos(429,267)\c&H24455F&}Seven times!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.85,0:15:10.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Seven times?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.14,0:15:13.48,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hanamoto's roommates were huge worrywarts...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.89,0:15:12.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\pos(569,272)}I've found you, Shuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.60,0:15:15.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\pos(436,283)}Hanamoto-kun! There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.48,0:15:18.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They'd go find and bring him back every time, so he couldn't stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.19,0:15:19.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor Tokudaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.53,0:15:21.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you so embarrassed about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.19,0:15:24.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I went on a self-realization journey when I was a student, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.28,0:15:27.62,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I went to Mongolia, Tibet, and India almost stark broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.12,0:15:34.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And while you were abroad, you published three\Nbooks, paid off all of your student loans...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.08,0:15:36.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And even rented your own research lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.13,0:15:42.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't liken such a trip filled with ambition\Nand goals to the holy journey of self-realization!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.47,0:15:46.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.10,0:15:48.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A pro?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.56,0:15:56.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I think we should just sit back and see\Nhow things go with Takemoto for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.56,0:15:56.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.56,0:15:58.73,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.11,0:16:01.15,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.53,0:16:06.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If Sensei went seven times and was\Nokay, Takemoto-kun should be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.91,0:16:08.70,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But Sensei went seven times—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.70,0:16:09.78,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all! Disperse!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.03,0:16:11.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Question!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.04,0:16:14.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find yourself on your journey of self-realization, Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.83,0:16:15.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Disperse!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.76,0:16:29.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot... did I fall asleep after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.14,0:16:33.77,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it was because I hadn't slept well for two nights in a row...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.77,0:16:40.52,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My hair's all crusty from the salt and sand...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.98,0:16:43.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And I stink of the ocean...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.50,0:17:04.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder... what I'm doing...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.72,0:17:08.18,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, I should contact everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.89,0:17:10.05,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet they're worried...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.64,0:17:16.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Or are they worried...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.86,0:17:25.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, we're gonna leave you behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.03,0:17:26.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.82,0:17:27.70,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it's cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.70,0:17:30.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't trip now, Kii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.53,0:17:32.12,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll be fine! Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.17,0:17:46.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing... my stomach's rumbling...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.30,0:17:48.68,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when I feel like crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.85,0:17:55.52,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,As I suspected, he's withdrawing money.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.22,0:17:57.93,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems he's alive, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.93,0:18:00.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't we find out where he withdrew the money?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.94,0:18:03.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think they'd give us that information.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.02,0:18:08.40,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's really like Takemoto to have this much saved up...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.40,0:18:12.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't drink, smoke, or play pachinko.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.45,0:18:13.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no mahjong either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.45,0:18:14.78,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And on top of that, no girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.99,0:18:18.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, no wonder he has money to spend.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.83,0:18:20.54,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If he doesn't have a girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.54,0:18:21.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, true!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.05,0:18:28.30,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, I know I started it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.30,0:18:31.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But something sharp like a knife is piercing my heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.93,0:18:34.39,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, the heart... me too...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.80,0:18:37.10,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, uh huh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.52,0:18:38.98,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.52,0:18:41.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess I'll put some money in for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.35,0:18:43.10,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.69,0:18:46.69,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a contribution. It's his pay for the month.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.23,0:18:50.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I bet Takemoto doesn't have any change\Nof clothes with him, much less a towel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.70,0:18:57.33,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,In terms of videogames, it's like going to a faraway\Ntown equipped only with rags and a wooden stick.
