Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.20,0:18:53.32,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnTimes New Roman\b0\fs30\fscx65\bord0\shad0\c&H8E8F8C&\pos(303,298)\frz33.553}DEF: 2
