Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.33,0:18:58.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What? That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.95,0:19:01.12,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The monsters will get him right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.12,0:19:04.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Me too! I need to send Takemoto some gold!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.75,0:19:09.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Like we said! If you support him this much, his\Nself-realization will become meaningless!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.51,0:19:16.43,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Note: {\be1\3c&H000000&}In Japan, post offices double as banks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.51,0:19:12.47,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\bord0.1\be1\fnFluid-Light\i1\fs21\frz12.254\c&H999B96&\3c&H91938E&\pos(562,110)}Post Office
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.84,0:19:14.80,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? It seems there's a little more...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.89,0:19:20.52,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! I'm so hungry that my stomach hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.52,0:19:21.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to eat something quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.71,0:19:48.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was little, one day I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.17,0:19:53.63,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,"How far can I go without turning back?"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.30,0:19:57.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what exactly I was trying to do at that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.76,0:20:00.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And myself now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.93,0:20:03.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I trying to do now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.35,0:20:06.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.03,0:20:17.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! Trucks drive this close to you inside tunnels?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.58,0:20:20.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.33,0:20:27.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally understood after screaming some.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.33,0:20:30.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd been afraid this whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.59,0:20:33.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I was afraid because I couldn't see my future.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.67,0:20:36.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I was afraid of not knowing what I wanted to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.72,0:20:40.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and of myself for not knowing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.35,0:20:42.27,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.81,0:20:50.77,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And I was afraid of the days that nevertheless\Nflew by without any mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.98,0:20:53.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.94,0:20:56.07,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Even then...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.21,0:21:12.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If I keep riding like this, will I be able to see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.67,0:21:17.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, even I...?
